 Visualize Security Findings with Matplotlib
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Create security data visualizations using Matplotlib and Python
Analyze security event patterns through graphical representations
Generate automated security reports with embedded charts
Interpret threat intelligence data using visual analytics
Apply data visualization best practices to cybersecurity contexts
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of fundamental cybersecurity concepts
Familiarity with Linux command-line operations
Basic knowledge of CSV data formats
